nodes.text: A type of moss existed on the planet Asusto. The moss was seemingly able to move by itself, and could entrap individuals who walked on it. When Jedi Master Lene Kostana and the Padawans Dooku and Sifo-Dyas visited Asusto in search of dark side artifacts, they were trapped by the moss and taken to the last coven of the Presagers of Hakotei, who wished to sacrifice them.
